description: Hi guys! Jiri is back after few months. Last time you saw me during football World Cup. I´ve had an accident and had to recover fully. But I´m back in full strength and with the dick, harder than before. Such a shame that summer is over, but what can one do. As I switched on the camera, I felt the thrill immediately. Out on the hunt. Didn´t have much luck with the first dude I´ve talked too, but I knew that the right one will come around. And I was right, I´ve stopped one young pal as he was leaving a post office. He kept smiling and answering all of my questions. I went straight for him and gave him my special offer. Something for something, in my case money for pleasure. He went for it. Small hotel room was just fine for me to release all energy I gathered during my recovery.
title: Czech Hunter 166
